              "description": {
                "paragraph": [
                  "With its Ion Core technology you get amazing power in every battery. Plus, they come pre-charged and ready to use. They are guaranteed to last for 10 years* in storage and they will hold a charge for up to 1 year when not in use. These powerful NiMH batteries work in any NiMH charger and you can recharge them up to 400 times. *or up to 400 recharges, whichever comes first."
                ],
                "descriptionLineSize": 2,
                "bullets": [
                  "DURACELL AAA RECHARGEABLE BATTERIES: The Duracell Rechargeable AAA battery is designed for use in video game controllers, wireless electronics, baby monitors, and more.",
